WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 4=

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:00.640
(Why is he sleeping here?)

00:01:19.310 --> 00:01:23.120
(This sachet is exactly the same
as the one in my dream.)

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.400
(Does he want to kill me?)

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:34.070
If you like my sachet,

00:01:34.950 --> 00:01:35.870
I can give it to you.

00:01:38.430 --> 00:01:39.510
We agreed last night

00:01:39.510 --> 00:01:40.640
to mind our own business.

00:01:41.430 --> 00:01:42.640
Why are you sleeping on my bed?

00:01:43.950 --> 00:01:45.150
Rules are dead;

00:01:46.070 --> 00:01:46.910
people are alive.

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:49.840
Do you want to live or die?

00:01:54.790 --> 00:01:55.950
Of course, I want to live.

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:01.920
Trying to kill your husband
right after the wedding?

00:02:02.870 --> 00:02:06.400
I fear the rumors might ruin your plans.

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:07.680
Mr. Huo.

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:09.120
Mrs. Huo.

00:02:12.030 --> 00:02:12.870
What is it?

00:02:13.032 --> 00:02:14.715
Physician Wang
from the Imperial Infirmary

00:02:14.726 --> 00:02:16.325
is here with the Emperor's oral decree.

00:02:16.520 --> 00:02:17.869
Hearing that Mrs. Huo is pregnant,

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:19.610
he came to help with her condition.

00:02:22.750 --> 00:02:23.590
What should we do?

00:02:25.590 --> 00:02:26.440
Useless.

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:27.840
How could you only report it now?

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.840
(Last night)

00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:29.680
I'm sorry, milady.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:30.840
I'm sorry, Master.

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:32.200
I'm sorry.

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.080
I'm sorry.

00:02:34.630 --> 00:02:35.470
So, Physician Zhang

00:02:36.150 --> 00:02:37.750
must've been bribed by that wretch.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.680
In that case,

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:44.150
I'll go invite Physician Wang.

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:45.910
I'd like to see

00:02:45.910 --> 00:02:47.150
how long Jiang Ruoli

00:02:47.310 --> 00:02:49.240
can keep hiding this.

00:03:06.630 --> 00:03:07.840
I heard Physician Wang is here.

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:09.120
May I ask the reason?

00:03:11.590 --> 00:03:12.430
Mr. Lu,

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:16.910
His Majesty heard about the news,

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:19.960
so he ordered me to come

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:21.190
to check Mrs. Huo's pulse.

00:03:21.630 --> 00:03:22.590
I see.

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:24.150
You must be busy.

00:03:24.430 --> 00:03:25.640
Why not let me guide the way

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:27.080
and take you to see her?

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:28.360
Sure.

00:03:31.910 --> 00:03:33.710
How thoughtful of you.

00:03:34.030 --> 00:03:35.800
Please lead the way.

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:36.840
Please.

00:03:39.313 --> 00:03:40.899
Are you sure he came to check her pulse?

00:03:41.030 --> 00:03:41.870
Yes.

00:03:41.980 --> 00:03:42.820
Where is he?

00:03:42.870 --> 00:03:43.910
He is waiting in the hall.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:54.360
Where is he?

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.710
Mr. Lu took Physician Wang

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:57.030
to Mrs. Huo's courtyard.

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.240
What?

00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:05.800
The pulse is smooth and steady.

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:08.590
Mrs. Huo has stable fetal energy.

00:04:08.590 --> 00:04:10.680
She only needs to rest peacefully.

00:04:11.470 --> 00:04:12.400
Thanks, Physician Wang.

00:04:34.270 --> 00:04:35.270
Ruyan,

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:36.560
Mrs. Huo instructed

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:38.070
that this pregnancy medicine

00:04:38.070 --> 00:04:39.460
should be poured out in secret.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.000
Alright, I understand.

00:04:41.163 --> 00:04:42.070
Go attend to your work.

00:04:42.070 --> 00:04:42.800
I'll deal with it.

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:43.760
Yes.

00:05:19.800 --> 00:05:21.040
Thanks to you today,

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:22.380
I was able to escape trouble.

00:05:22.630 --> 00:05:23.470
It's nothing.

00:05:24.630 --> 00:05:26.000
How did you know

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:27.680
that Ruyan was pregnant?

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:28.920
I only learned it by chance.

00:05:33.430 --> 00:05:34.270
Ruoli,

00:05:34.830 --> 00:05:36.303
a false pregnancy is no small matter.

00:05:36.630 --> 00:05:37.759
You may hide it for a while,

00:05:37.770 --> 00:05:38.480
but not forever.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:39.870
You and Yanzhi...

00:05:40.070 --> 00:05:40.910
Don't worry.

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:42.013
I know what I'm doing.

00:05:43.920 --> 00:05:44.800
If you need help,

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:45.840
just say the word.

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:48.270
Thank you.

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:51.640
Between you and me,

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.386
no need for such courtesy.

00:06:24.390 --> 00:06:25.230
Hey.

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:27.950
Did you hear about what happened

00:06:27.950 --> 00:06:28.800
in the mansion today?

00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:30.680
Don't even mention it.

00:06:31.070 --> 00:06:32.830
Someone ignorant of the rules

00:06:33.190 --> 00:06:35.270
tried to clean the heir's study.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:36.733
In broad daylight,

00:06:36.744 --> 00:06:37.701
their legs were broken,

00:06:37.712 --> 00:06:38.706
and they were thrown out.

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:40.870
The heir's study

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:41.800
is a forbidden place.

00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:42.920
Except for Shitou,

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:43.813
no one can go near it.

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:44.870
Exactly.

00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:46.600
Clean properly.

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:47.440
I'll go clean there.

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:52.070
(A forbidden place.)

00:07:01.510 --> 00:07:04.480
(Huo Linchuan is hiding something.)

00:08:09.070 --> 00:08:10.630
Dear, what are you looking for?

00:08:14.530 --> 00:08:15.390
I...

00:08:15.390 --> 00:08:17.510
Are you here to bathe with me?

00:08:45.030 --> 00:08:45.870
Assassin!

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.406
- Catch the assassin!
- Catch them!

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:50.240
Catch the assassin!

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:51.120
- Over there!
- Hurry!

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.400
- Catch the assassin!
- Hurry!

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:13.790
The assassin might still be here.

00:09:17.750 --> 00:09:18.840
You haven't answered me.

00:09:20.150 --> 00:09:22.150
Why did you appear in my study?

00:09:24.150 --> 00:09:27.630
Do you really want to become my wife?

00:09:28.840 --> 00:09:29.680
Yanzhi.

00:09:33.750 --> 00:09:34.590
Yanzhi.

00:09:37.150 --> 00:09:37.990
Yanzhi,

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:39.670
I heard there was an assassin.

00:09:40.270 --> 00:09:41.110
Are you alright?

00:09:50.600 --> 00:09:51.670
Don't worry.

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:52.910
I'm fine.

00:09:56.960 --> 00:09:57.910
Really?

00:09:58.600 --> 00:09:59.440
Then...

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:00.920
Where is Ruoli?

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:02.550
Why haven't I seen her?

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:07.510
You need not worry

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:10.030
about my wife.

00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:13.720
Am I right?

00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:17.580
Since everything is fine,

00:10:18.910 --> 00:10:20.360
I'll take my leave.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:36.030
Huo Linchuan, don't go too far.

00:10:36.630 --> 00:10:37.470
Jiang Ruoli,

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:39.670
don't forget

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:44.240
that you are now my wife.

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:13.670
Mr. Huo, we've checked everything.

00:11:13.790 --> 00:11:15.080
No clues were left behind.

00:11:20.870 --> 00:11:21.720
(It seems)

00:11:22.270 --> 00:11:24.080
(I must seek Ruoli's help.)

00:11:49.520 --> 00:11:51.040
♪The dream shattered♪

00:11:51.400 --> 00:11:53.080
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:11:53.080 --> 00:11:54.720
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:11:55.600 --> 00:11:57.160
♪How vague♪

00:11:57.560 --> 00:11:59.080
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:01.320
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:04.720
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:08.040
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:13.440
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:12:14.040 --> 00:12:15.560
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:19.520
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:21.800
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:25.920
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:12:26.640 --> 00:12:29.480
♪Life after life♪

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:32.640
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:12:33.280 --> 00:12:37.360
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:40.480
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:12:40.640 --> 00:12:42.040
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:12:42.040 --> 00:12:45.160
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:46.680
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:50.560
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:12:51.280 --> 00:12:54.080
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:57.200
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:12:57.520 --> 00:13:01.920
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:05.080
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:09.640
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:13:09.840 --> 00:13:15.560
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:18.720
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:13:18.960 --> 00:13:21.680
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:28.120
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪